One more comment.  In hindsight, it looks to me like the original poster saw
both NeXT's announcement about releasing the *specifications* and Sun's
announcement about their *implementation*, and either got them confused or
jumped to conclusions.  This may merely have been a problem with bad timing
(e.g. they may have arrived at virtually the same time, thereby implying a
nonexistent relationship).

